        ================
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/mopidy-tachikoma.svg
            :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Mopidy-Tachikoma/
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/palfrey/mopidy-tachikoma.svg?branch=master
